{"type": "article", "id": 30705, "title": "Hugo Boss 季度利润暴跌，以及，奥运会队服一览看这里 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-08T02:21:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 20242, "name": "里约奥运会"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 2910, "name": "Hugo Boss"}, {"id": 3111, "name": "Giorgio Armani"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 102, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160808002605pWBF6D1TSnvqLUPy.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/hugo-boss-q2-income-10502191/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugo Boss 第二季度净利润暴跌</a></b> | Hugo Boss 第二季净利润大跌 84%，其 CEO Mark Langer 表示，将在未来的 18 个月内关闭全球 20 家业绩较差的门店。</p><p class=\"\"><b></b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/giorgio-armani-moves-spring-show-september-schedule-milan-10501481/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Giorgio Armani 将退出 9 月米兰时装周的闭幕秀</b> </a>| 9月份的米兰时装周，Giorgio Armani 不会走闭幕秀，把闭幕秀的位置留给另一个国际品牌。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.foliomag.com/2016/time-inc-readjusts-forecasted-growth-2016-1-5-percent/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Time 时代集团调低了 2016 年度营收预期 </b></a>| 纸媒表现不力，Time 将此前的 1％－5% 的增长预期调整至 1.5%。</p><p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/l-brands-july-sales-10501521/\" rel=\"nofollow\">维多利亚的秘密母公司 L Brands 7 月销售超预期</a> </b>| 二季度L Brands 集团同店销售增3%，Victoria’s Secret 维多利亚的秘密和Bath &amp; Body Works 分别增2%和5%。L Brands 集团表示，8月份将聚焦于Pink 系列的返校季和Victoria’s Secret 维多利亚的秘密“lounge bra” 新品的销售。</p><h3><i>一些值得一看的：</i></h3><p class=\"\">这次里约奥运会的国家队服，我们为你挑选了一些不错的品牌设计。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/hm-goes-green-with-olympic-ceremony-flag-bearers-outfit-10502228/\" rel=\"nofollow\">H&amp;M for 瑞典。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808003512olSmApj8FLTaNGrB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808003522nZ7pTIa0toqxKmY3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/laurens-olympic-fundraiser-10502812/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ralph Lauren for 美国。</a><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808004004O9DUtHfJsFXdWxnw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808004013iFNsUxGvAJ6epZWT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Lacoste for 法国。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808004023l0uY7xZP1jnrb3EN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808004032Empzf2Bdj1XqKn38.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Christian Louboutin for 古巴。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808004045uRZytF7nWGM521wx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608080040549aOIkKmClXdJ1xTW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Stella McCartney for 英国。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608080041089bPlC4MRy6cHkBOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666454\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808004117B4wnyi8YGT1kZgEo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">以及，英国奢侈时尚环保品牌<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/bottletop-designs-costumes-rio-2016-opening-ceremony-10502315/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> bottletop</a> 为里约奥运会开幕式设计了服装。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808094401sMUKZ1rtB3mC5LfW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334961\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808094409mX0ivPRa6CrpITtZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334961\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">美国品牌&nbsp; Rebecca Taylor 推出了更为平易近人的副线 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/rebecca-taylor-launches-cheaper-line-la-vie/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">La Vie</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608081022267eAR69HWt0kfansM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808102234BkcTHY9oKQy6hXax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">超模 Naomi Campbell 演绎 Rihanna 最新的 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/naomi-campbell-fronts-rihannas-fenty-puma-2016-fall-winter-campaign\" rel=\"nofollow\">FENTY PUMA 特辑</a>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608081022036RPBWUXvp8MJrnyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667129\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608081022165fTjzVEYMJd3kHGu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/nikelab-kobe-xi-elite-low-brazil\" rel=\"nofollow\">NikeLab 推出里约奥运主题配色的&nbsp;Kobe X